    "message": "fix: skip default HEARTBEAT_OK instructions when custom prompt is set\n\nWhen a custom heartbeat prompt is configured (agents.defaults.heartbeat.prompt),\nthe default HEARTBEAT_OK instructions should not be added to the system prompt.\nCustom prompts define their own heartbeat behavior, and having both the custom\nprompt and the default instructions causes conflicting guidance.\n\nThis enables the 'Free Mind Protocol' pattern where agents can define custom\nheartbeat behavior that doesn't require HEARTBEAT_OK responses.\n\nFixes issue where custom heartbeat prompt was being combined with hardcoded\nHEARTBEAT_OK instructions, leading to confusing agent behavior.",
